           <hr />
           <h1>
            About Me
            <span class="gray">
             &gt; Clock Making and Clock Repair
            </span>
           </h1>
           <p>
           </p>
           <p>
           </p>
           <p>
            I have been interested in all things mechanical since childhood. Having a scrap yard a short distance from our garden fence no doubt fed this interest, and I spent many happy hours playing among war surplus machinery, steam rollers and vintage cars when my Mother thought that I was safe in the garden.
           </p>
          </blockquote>
         </th>
         <th width="192" align="right" scope="col">
          <embed width="200" height="200" quality="high" wmode="transparent" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" src="http://www.adamdorman.com/flash/aa_watch.swf">
          </embed>
         </th>
